file.name: xml_payload_with_ref.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenApi Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
tags:
  - name: pets
    description: Pets Tag
  - name: list
    description: List Tag

paths:
  /pets:
    post:
      summary: Create a pet
      operationId: createPet
      tags:
        - pets
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/xml:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
        description: Pet data
        required: true
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        tag:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/pets": post: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [application/xml]
